1) Jessie M. Monroe Elmentary School is located less than 1 mile
from the studied intersection and was in session on the date of
the count, as were all Brunswick County Schools.
2) As requested, U-turns were counted instead of pedestrians.
4) Area lighting was not present at the count location.
5) No highway construction was observed that impacted normal
6) Data collection equipment was operating correctly at time of
7) Counter took breaks from 9:45 – 10:00 AM, 1:15 – 1:45 PM, and
6:30 – 6:45 PM. Data for these periods was interpolated.
8) Counter Notes: No emergency vehicles with activated lights and/or sirens were observed during this count.
Also, there was no posted speed limit on Pea Landing Road or Thomasboro Road.
